Run! Run!

717
00:51:09,378 --> 00:51:11,778
You got guts, Roarke.

718
00:51:13,916 --> 00:51:17,613
But you shouldn't have
broken your promise about the gun.

719
00:51:19,888 --> 00:51:22,686
Friends don't do that.

720
00:51:26,495 --> 00:51:28,793
I thought you were a nice guy.

721
00:51:28,864 --> 00:51:32,163
I am a nice guy.

722
00:51:33,235 --> 00:51:35,897
Just a different kind
of nice guy.

723
00:51:45,314 --> 00:51:49,410
Damn, Terry.
Looks like we lose our deposit.

724
00:51:49,484 --> 00:51:52,544
[Wade Laughing]
All right!

725
00:51:52,621 --> 00:51:55,351
Now that I'm head of the family,
here's what we're gonna do!

726
00:51:55,424 --> 00:52:00,225
We're gonna haul ass down this river.
No more fishing. No more sightseeing.

727
00:52:00,295 --> 00:52:04,095
And unfortunately,
no more skinny dipping.

728
00:52:04,166 --> 00:52:05,599
- By the way, Gail...
- [Clicking]

729
00:52:05,667 --> 00:52:08,227
You're gonna get another chance
to run the Gauntlet.

730
00:52:08,303 --> 00:52:11,670
- We're not stopping at Bridle Creek.
- What?

731
00:52:11,740 --> 00:52:16,268
That's right. Come on, let's get
this shit up the hill and outta sight!

732
00:52:20,215 --> 00:52:22,740
Roarke.

733
00:52:22,818 --> 00:52:25,412
Were you takin'
pictures of me?

734
00:52:26,355 --> 00:52:28,550
Give me that camera.

735
00:52:30,425 --> 00:52:32,757
[Sighing]
